Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Liella,,0,0,0,,-----------------Liella no uta-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:06.11,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}小路旁的阴影处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:09.82,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}我发现一道暗门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:13.58,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}满心欢喜将它打开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:17.16,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}却被传回了起点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:20.96,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}没有关系 重新出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:24.71,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}是你鼓励的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:32.76,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}给了我再次前进的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:36.27,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}是捷径？ 还是绕远？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:40.27,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}谁知道呢 先试试看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.65,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}我们一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:48.40,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}不断地挑战迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:53.20,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}偶尔走错路也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.70,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}不会有任何惧怕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:01.37,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}尽管迷宫中如此黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.42,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}我们最后也一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:08.51,Liella,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9911D8&\blur3}成就更坚强的自己
